locations: New York City, New York, USA
imdb.plot outline: Each episode of Good Exposure portrays a different stage in the seasonal shelf life of a male model. We follow the New Face, Supermodel and Former Coverboy to castings, photoshoots, fashion shows and walking lessons - depicting scenes and situations that truly exist in the world of high fashion, but until now, have never been portrayed for their true absurdity.
